            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>转扩周知！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%9224%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%90%83%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%9224%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%90%83%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生提醒24小时吃遍一座城不可取#</span></a>】国庆假期，“极限24小时吃遍某城”挑战走红网络。医生提醒，这样的饮食状态不可取。各类高油高脂、辛辣刺激的食物混杂下肚，极易打乱肠胃消化“生物钟”，增加消化道负担，引起腹痛、呕吐等症状。同时，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%8A%82%E5%81%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9A%B4%E9%A5%AE%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%9F%E6%98%93%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%83%B0%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%8A%82%E5%81%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9A%B4%E9%A5%AE%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%9F%E6%98%93%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%83%B0%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#节假日暴饮暴食易引发急性胰腺炎#</span></a>，重度胰腺炎还易引起多脏器功能衰竭。假期饮食该注意什么？看↓<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4953400618450950" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hik3f05nktj62yo1o0hdu02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dGbquTcX